                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>I<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>N<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>T<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>A<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>O<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="6" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>S<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="7" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>A<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="8" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>M<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="9" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>T<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="10" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>I<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="11" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>X<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="12" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>T<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Schreibtechnik: litterae aureae (von außen eingedübelt); erhalten sind noch mehrere Fragmente einer Tafel sowie zwölf Buchstaben (Dicke ca. 0,1 cm). Buchstabenhöhe: I, N, T, weniger sicher auch A, O, S: 8,8-9 cm (vielleicht zu Anto[n]i[nus] zu ergänzen?); A, M, T, I(?): 8,6 cm; X, T(?): 7,5 cm. Nach Kaschuba aufgrund der Fundlage zu einer einzigen Lagertorinschrift gehörig. (B): CIL 03, 13543; Kaschuba: kleinere Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
